Text: NYU Stern in Houstoncase you have not yet received your invitation it is not too late to attend We would love to meet you in person Please join Dean Daly of the Stern School Mary Miller Associate Dean and area alumni and find out why New York Universitys Stern School of Business can take you where you want to go MBA Program Information Session Houston Wednesday November pm Enron Allen Center Smith Street th Floor The Forum Houston TX Special thanks to Enron for generously sponsoring this event Space is limited and will be filled in order of response Please RSVP by via email fax or our Web site Fax Please include the city name your name daytime telephone number and email address Email Please include the city name in the subject line and your name daytime telephone number and email address in the message text Web site wwwsternnyuedumbaadmissionsfulltimerecruit Click on RSVP and please include the city name in the subject line and your name daytime telephone number and email address in the message jmartinvcf
